description: The Demographic Inquiry API provides developers with access to current year estimates and five year projections for 700+ demographic variables.  Categories include population summaries, income characteristics, consumer expenditures, educational attainment, and demographic profiles.  We also provide multiple ways (GIS and Non-GIS Based methods) to extract data of interest.   Operations include inquiry by point, buffer (proximity), and travel time.  Data coverage includes the Contiguous US, Alaska, and Hawaii.
